videos.description: Ryan Willis finds Eric Kumah for a 21-yard Virginia Tech touchdown.
videos.headline: Virginia Tech strikes first with 21-yd TD

videos.description: Desmond Ridder makes a short pass to Charles McClelland, who weaves through the defense and runs 38 yards for a Cincinnati touchdown.
videos.headline: Cincinnati ties game with 38-yd TD

videos.description: Michael Warren II fumbles the ball in the end zone, and Kahlil Lewis recovers it to give the Bearcats a 13-7 lead.
videos.headline: Cincinnati recovers fumble in end zone for TD

videos.description: Steven Peoples squeezes into the end zone for a 1-yard Hokies touchdown to tie Cincinnati.
videos.headline: Virginia Tech answers back with 1-yd TD

videos.description: Michael Warren II runs untouched into the end zone for a 40-yard Cincinnati touchdown.
videos.headline: Warren bursts for 40-yd Cincy TD

videos.description: Ryan Willis throws to Chris Cunningham for a 2-yard touchdown, putting the Hokies back on top over the Bearcats.
videos.headline: Willis connects with Cunningham for 2-yard Virginia Tech TD

videos.description: Cincinnati QB Hayden Moore breaks through the defense and runs in for a 19-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Moore puts Cincinnati back on top with TD run

videos.description: Virginia Tech QB Ryan Willis fakes a pass and runs into the end zone for a 5-yard score.
videos.headline: Virginia Tech's Willis responds with 5-yd TD run

videos.description: Michael Warren II gives Cincinnati a late lead after running into the end zone for an 8-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Cincy's Warren II runs for 8-yard TD
